<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy - Code Preview Live</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #2563EB;
            --gray-50: #f8f9fa;
            --gray-100: #f3f4f6;
            --gray-200: #e5e7eb;
            --gray-600: #4b5563;
            --gray-800: #1f2937;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: var(--gray-800);
            background: var(--gray-50);
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 60px 20px;
        }

        .header {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .last-updated {
            color: var(--gray-600);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .content {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .section {
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        .section:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            color: var(--gray-800);
        }

        ul {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: var(--gray-800);
        }

        .emphasis {
            background: var(--gray-100);
            padding: 16px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--gray-600);
        }

        a {
            color: var(--primary);
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
            <div class="last-updated">Last updated: <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString() %></div>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="section">
                <h2>Overview</h2>
                <p>Code Preview Live is a browser extension that helps users preview HTML and Mermaid code while browsing. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your data.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <h2>Data Collection</h2>
                <p>We collect the following data when you use our extension:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Code snippets that you choose to preview</li>
                    <li>Basic usage statistics (number of previews, types of code rendered)</li>
                </ul>
                <div class="emphasis">
                    <p><strong>Important:</strong> We only collect code that you explicitly choose to preview. We do not collect any other content from the websites you visit.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <h2>How We Use Your Data</h2>
                <p>The collected data is used for:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Generating code previews</li>
                    <li>Improving the extension's performance</li>
                    <li>Debugging and error tracking</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <h2>Data Storage</h2>
                <p>Code snippets are:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Stored temporarily for preview generation</li>
                    <li>Automatically deleted after 24 hours</li>
                    <li>Never shared with third parties</li>
                    <li>Stored securely on our servers</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <h2>Your Rights</h2>
                <p>You have the right to:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Access your data</li>
                    <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
                    <li>Opt out of data collection</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <h2>Security</h2>
                <p>We protect your data through:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Secure HTTPS connections</li>
                    <li>Regular security audits</li>
                    <li>Limited data retention</li>
                    <li>Access controls and encryption</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <h2>Contact Us</h2>
                <p>If you have any questions about our privacy policy or data practices, please contact us at:</p>
                <p><a href="mailto:privacy@jobsum.works">privacy@jobsum.works</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Code Preview Live. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p><a href="/">Back to home</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 